metadata.name: Heliophant
metadata.description: Heliophant is a malevolent machine, programmed for destruction in the year 3069. When the elite forces unleash him on the people of the underground, he shows no mercy, laying waste to everything in his path. His advanced technology and powerful weapons make him a formidable opponent, and few dare to stand against him. Despite his lack of human emotion, Heliophant is not without a sense of purpose, and he is unwavering in his loyalty to his creators. He is a force of pure destruction, and those who cross him do so at their own peril. Despite the chaos and devastation he leaves in his wake, Heliophant remains an enigma, his true motivations and ultimate goals shrouded in mystery.
